fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: "A sigh. "You are thinking about thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sigh. "You are thinking about this metaphor too literally..."

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""But we shouldn't overstate their i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But we shouldn't overstate their importance. They are simply one of many tools used by the Moralintern to set policy."

fields.Title: You: ""This is... a lot to take in.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is... a lot to take in."

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""Oh, there are many things you can..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, there are many things you can do. If you're interested in learning how to canvass for signatures, manage a polling place, or register voters, the Commission would be more than happy to direct you to a workshop..."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "All major cities in EPIS-aligned na..."
fields.Dialogue Text: All major cities in EPIS-aligned nations, you can't help but notice.

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""Acknowledged. We are at your dispo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Acknowledged. We are at your disposal."

fields.Title: You: ""What do these 'wings' represent?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do these 'wings' represent?"

fields.Title: You: ""But what if I *want* someone else..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But what if I *want* someone else to make all my decisions for me?"

fields.Title: You: "(Whisper.) "Hey, Kim. Why haven't y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Whisper.) "Hey, Kim. Why haven't you joined the Ethics Division?"

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""It may be. We're only a second sig..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It may be. We're only a second signaller, not a metaphysician. It's a rather cold way to think about the world, isn't it?"

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""Not only that, but you, you are al..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Not only that, but you, you are also part of that centuries-long plan. When you cross one of the open plazas, your own shadow is effortlessly woven into the great latticework, a deliberate synthesis of humanity, art, and the natural world."

fields.Title: You: "Wait, what's this 'better way'?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait, what's this 'better way'?

fields.Title: Coalition Warship Archer: ""Is everything alright?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is everything alright?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant gives a long sigh as..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant gives a long sigh as he removes his headphones. There's relief on his face as he turns toward you.

fields.Title: You: ""Built for *me*?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Built for *me*?"
